Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the locomotion task of a humanoid robot and proposes a framework to build a memory of motion to warm-start an optimal control solver. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper formulates the learning problem as a regression problem to predict a single-step motion given the desired contact locations. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve vision-based perception for the locomotion task. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also less likely but possible as the paper proposes a framework that involves learning and optimization. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also possible as the paper deals with optimal control and warm-starting techniques.
